  "description": "Resource consumption broken down by namespace: which namespaces burn the most CPU and memory, how many pods each runs, and how close they sit to their ResourceQuota. Answers \"which team is eating the cluster?\" and \"who is about to hit their quota?\" from kube-state-metrics and cAdvisor.",
